# Canonical contributor identities.
# Collapses each person's multiple name/email variants into ONE identity so
# `git shortlog -sne` and GitHub's Contributors graph show an accurate per-person
# commit count. Non-destructive: does not rewrite history — git applies it at read time.
#
# Format:  Canonical Name <canonical@email>  Commit Name <commit@email>

